    <description>Expose is a flexible and powerful rapid development theme framework for joomla 2.5 and 3.x with a very small footprint provides an extensible environment for developing, maintaining, and deploying high quality themes. Choosing Expose allows you to release your themes earlier, host and scale them without problem, and maintain them over time with no hassle.
